Package: container-runner
Architecture: all
Depends: docker-ce (>= 20.10) | docker.io (>= 20.10),
         docker-compose-plugin (>= 2.0) | docker-compose (>= 2.0),
         python3 (>= 3.8),
         python3-yaml,
         systemd
Description: Container Runner for Samsung Humanoid Robots
 Manages Docker containers for robot services (rise, rise-dashboard,
 whole-body-controller) based on the ROBOT_MODEL configured on each robot.
 .
 Features:
  - Automatic service selection based on ROBOT_MODEL
  - Docker image pulling from BART registry
  - Systemd service management via Docker Compose
  - Per-model image version overrides
